{"tid":1418772,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"我成日俾催淚彈打中，我有啲嘢想分享","createTime":"2019-08-05T20:21:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T06:07:29.000Z","uid":34205,"like":89,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"6cb48f722789a01d659304f0fee1dfea9b9c984c","tid":1418772,"uid":34205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T20:21:48.000Z","msg":"我呢個月都係喺前線攞盾擋子彈<br />\n次次都唔小心中彈<br />\n講緊係粒鐵打中身呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲要身體對催淚彈反應大<br />\n次次都俾人以為我唔得<br />\n出親去到都chur剩半條人命返屋企<br />\n<br />\n做前線係咪好威呢？<br />\n自覺少少啦<br />\n着曬裝成個ironman咁喺人群度行<br />\n戀權，又未到嘅，但係自我彭漲好正常<br />\n直頭想有張委任證俾人知我係前線添啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但係未開戰嘅時候我做緊咩呢？<br />\n搬鐵馬，落雨開下遮呢啲好正常<br />\n<br />\n更多嘅係會周圍做下啲PR嘢<br />\n同啲街坊傾下計拉攏下<br />\n幫下路過嘅人，調停下紛爭<br />\n仲有就係清下啲垃圾<br />\n雖然睇落好無謂，但係好重要<br />\n<br />\n係，宜家勇武升級係好成功<br />\n但係唔好因為勇武而忘記咗本身成功嘅起點<br />\n<br />\n香港示威者可以受國際讚賞就係因為和理非啲PR門面做得好<br />\n<br />\n老黑要打，但係唔好打到血肉模糊<br />\n盡量打身，斷一隻手或腳就ok<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n狗係抵死，屋企人都好唔曬<br />\n但係記住嗰棟唔係<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">警察宿舍</span></span><br />\n係<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">紀律部隊宿舍</span></span><br />\n有好撚型嘅消防，救護同海關叔叔住㗎！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我地行到今日絕對係靠勇武手足衝返嚟<br />\n尊重係必須<br />\n<br />\n但係勇武對警黑以外嘅人要放鬆啲<br />\n佢地唔會傷害我地<br />\n唔洗有惡意敵意<br />\n<br />\n勇武都可以同需要有溫柔<br />\n可以嘅，喺面罩下俾啲微笑<br />\n雖然對某啲手足嚟講係好on9<br />\n但係對方會feel到<br />\n最重要想大家記得<span style=\"font-size: large;\">唔洗下下咁肉緊</span><br />\n<br />\n效率重要，PR同時重要<br />\n<br />\n兄弟爬山，各有各做<br />\n一定唔可以失平衡<br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"1eed416ca8258aebf90e2483640a70cdf2faf911","tid":1418772,"uid":46223,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T20:35:47.000Z","msg":"勇武派我愛你"},{"pid":"f3a120558048414f09db66b86d7e1ddc2d51dbdd","tid":1418772,"uid":75148,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T20:38:06.000Z","msg":"不割蓆！放核彈都不割蓆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e5eea7b6b2daae8c2f7f61c31ead5b6a57c21c4","tid":1418772,"uid":145156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T20:40:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ebd59021313d5705fcbb66be133569447ca2e82","tid":1418772,"uid":218646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T20:46:10.000Z","msg":"推 起碼要碎一邊膝頭"},{"pid":"7d927dfeb940fa8ee2ac5d26208c65796fc5c90c","tid":1418772,"uid":122083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T20:46:30.000Z","msg":"老黑唔好打頭同身<br />\n同我狠狠地專攻下身<br />\n打到佢殘廢春袋都打爆佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a03328e29dfd26b9541c1f8af69e4ac810ce34f","tid":1418772,"uid":135867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T20:47:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rNOxBrP.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrNOxBrP.gif&h=672c8b5c&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bDJNqkb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbDJNqkb.gif&h=27f2be48&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://streamable.com/igroa\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstreamable.com%2Figroa&d=bDHmYwogulq9FkNLxWxOtiHJFIlRN37b%2BuZTNWj4Tkw%3D&h=229b3bb1\" target=\"_blank\">https://streamable.com/igroa</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JY7TMXRzZOY&amp;feature=youtu.be\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DJY7TMXRzZOY%26feature%3Dyoutu.be&d=bDHmYwogulq9FkNLxWxOtiHJFIlRN37b%2BuZTNWj4Tkw%3D&h=5b86c2a5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.